<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>This time of the year, we'd usually be shopping for holiday essentials. But with the coronavirus lockdown and more of us working from home than ever, we've been stocking up on soft and cosy clothes to lounge around the house in.</p>

<p>One item that hordes of shoppers are picking up is this ultra-soft, comfortable and oversized hoodie blanket from Amazon.</p>

<p>Imagine your favourite hoodie and your softest blanket merged. That's precisely what the Sienna Sherpa Hooded Blanket is. Reviewers call it 'very comfy', 'cosy' and compare wearing it to 'a great big snuggly bear hug!'</p>

<p>This oversized hoodie blanket lined with sherpa fleece has accumulated hundreds of reviews on Amazon</p>

<p>Due to the recent drop in temperatures, the blanket hoodie, which costs as little as £16.99 depending on the colour you select, has seen a jump in sales. </p>

<p>It's currently the number one bestselling item in Amazon's Women's Hoodies category - and it's easy to see why shoppers love it.</p>

<p>The oversized hoodie blanket lined with sherpa fleece (designed to mimic the warmth and comfort of sheepskin) has accumulated hundreds of reviews so far with 84 per cent of them rating the bestseller a full five stars.</p>

<p>And there's no doubt its popularity will surge with winter on the horizon. One customer wrote: 'It's going to be great in the cold winter months to curl up and watch a film.'</p>

<p>Another shopper added: 'Absolute heaven! Super soft and thick for those extra cold evenings! Baby pink is very cute. Nice and baggy so it cuddles you.'</p>

<p>Reviewers call the hoodie blanket 'very comfy', 'cosy' and compare wearing it to 'a great big snuggly bear hug'</p>

<p>The one size fits all snug hoodie from Sienna includes a large, oversized front pocket and elastic cuffs, and it can be machine washed. You can pick it up in either blush pink, charcoal grey, or silver grey.</p>

<p>'WOW. I bought this for my daughter (for her birthday so not given it to her yet), but I know she'll LOVE it,' one parent wrote in their review. </p>

<p>'It's super soft, cosy, comfy, cuddly and everything else. I ended up buying myself one and one for my daughter's best friend for Christmas. These are awesome.'</p>

<p>Another reviewer said: 'Bought two of these, one for myself and the other for my girlfriend, we both love them, good size, really comfy and warm, great quality.'</p>

